  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tew ne buhs nokant.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tew ne buhs Laulibu\npahrkahpt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Untew ne buhs sagt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tew ne buhs nepateefu\nLeezibu doht prett tawu Tuwakut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Untew ne buhs eekahroht\ntawa Tuwaka Seewu. Un tew\nne buhs eekahroht tawa Tuwaka\nNammu/ winna Tihrumu/ nedś\nwinna Kalpu/ nedś winna Kalpo-\nni/ winna Wehrţi/ nedś winna\nChseli/ nedś wiffu/ kas tawam\nTuwakam peederr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schohs Wahrdus runna-\nja tas KUNGS us wiffu juhsfu\nDraudst Kalnā/ no Ugguns Ba-\ndebbes un Krehstibas Widdus ar\nleelu Balkfni/ un ne peelikke ne\nneeka klahtu/ un winch rakstija\ntohs us diwi akurinaixeem Gal-\ndixteem/ un dewe man tohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad juhs to Balkfni no\ntahs Tumfibus Widdus dsirde-\njat/un tas Kalns ar Ugguni dedse/\ntad peegahjat juhs pee man wiffi\nWirfneeki juhsfu Ziltu/ un juhsfu\nWezzajee/ un fazzijat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Raugi/ tas KUNGS\nmuhsfu Deews irr mums rahdijs\nfawu Gohdibu/ un fawu Augsti-\nbu/ nn mehs effam winna Balk-\nfni no Ugguns Widdus dsirdej-\nfchi. Schodeen effam mehs re-\ndsejfschi Deewn ar Zilwekeein run-\nnajam/ un tee dshwi paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet nu/kapehz buhs mums\nnomirt/ jo schis leels Ugguns\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo kas irr wiffa Meefa/ ta\nwarretu ta dsihwa Deew\nBalkfni dsirdeht no Ugguns Wid-\ndus runnajam/ itt ka mehs/ u\neffam dsihwi palikkuschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pee-eij tu/ un klanfaj\nwiffu/ ko tas KUNGS muhs\nDeews runnahs/ un runna tu u\nmums wiffu/ ko tas KUNG\nmuhsfu Deews us tew runnahs\ntad gribbam mehs klanfijht/ u\nto darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas KUNGS juhs fu Wahrdnu Balkfni dsirdeja/ juhs us man runnajat/ tad faz-\nzija tas KUNGS us man: Eefimu scho Lauscho Wahrdnu Balkfni dsirdejs/ko tee us tew irr run-\nnajschi/tee irr labbi darrijfschi/ a\nwiffu/ ko tee irr runnajschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ak faut winneem tahd\nSirde buhtu man bihteēs/ u\nwiffus mannis Banflus turreh-\nmuhscham/ ka winneem labb\nkiahtohs/ un winnu Behrneen\nmuhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Etj/fakki us teem: Atgree-\nseetees us juhfeem Dshwoftteem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tu stahwi fscheit pe-\nman/ ka es us tew runnaju wi-\nfus tohs Banflus/ un wiffu\nLikfumus/ un Teefas/ ko tew win-\nneem buhs mahziht/ ka tee ta da-\nra tai Semme/ ko es teem dohm\nwinneem eemantoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nemmneet tad wehra/ k\njuhs\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
